    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="新建页面"><a href="#新建页面" class="headerlink" title="新建页面"></a>新建页面</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new page xxxxx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="清理"><a href="#清理" class="headerlink" title="清理"></a>清理</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo cl</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="本地调试"><a href="#本地调试" class="headerlink" title="本地调试"></a>本地调试</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="生成页面"><a href="#生成页面" class="headerlink" title="生成页面"></a>生成页面</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="上传项目"><a href="#上传项目" class="headerlink" title="上传项目"></a>上传项目</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="追番数据"><a href="#追番数据" class="headerlink" title="追番数据"></a>追番数据</h3><h4 id="更新追番数据"><a href="#更新追番数据" class="headerlink" title="更新追番数据"></a>更新追番数据</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo bangumis -u</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="删除追番数据"><a href="#删除追番数据" class="headerlink" title="删除追番数据"></a>删除追番数据</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo bangumis -d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>项目地址：<a href="https://github.com/mmdjiji/hexo-bangumis">https://github.com/mmdjiji/hexo-bangumis</a></p><h3 id="bilibili卡片"><a href="#bilibili卡片" class="headerlink" title="bilibili卡片"></a>bilibili卡片</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% bilicard your_video_id %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>项目地址：<a href="https://github.com/MaxChang3/hexo-bilibili-card">https://github.com/MaxChang3/hexo-bilibili-card</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
